data.comment: The match is underway at Strandvallen.
In the minute 2, Throw-in Mjallby.
Varbergs take a 0-1 lead thanks to Robin Book.

Can Mjallby get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Varbergs's half?

That's a fine assist from Adama Fofana.

Viktor Agardius instrumental with a fine assist.

In the minute 69, Free kick Varbergs.

Goal! The home team draw level at 2-2 through Jacob Bergstrom.
In the minute 76, Max Watson with an assist there.
Mjallby awarded a throw-in in their own half.

Mjallby are pushing forward but Besard Sabovic's finish is wide of the goal.
Ball goes out of play for a Varbergs goal kick.
In the minute 79, Goal! Albin Winbo gives Varbergs a 2-3 lead in Hallevik.
Great play from Anton Liljenback to set up the goal.
Throw-in for Mjallby in their own half.
In the minute 81, Play has been temporarily suspended for attention to Jon Birkfeldt for Varbergs who is writhing in pain on the pitch.

Goal kick for Varbergs at Strandvallen.
In the minute 83, Can Varbergs get the ball into an attacking position from this throw-in in Mjallby's half?

In the minute 84, Mjallby have been awarded a corner by Fredrik Klitte.
Jesper Gustavsson for Mjallby gets in a strike but fails to hit the target.

Fredrik Klitte awards the away team a throw-in.
Throw-in for Mjallby in the half of Varbergs.

The 2nd half is prolonged by 3 minutes of added time.
Free kick for Mjallby in their own half.
Ball goes out of play for a Varbergs goal kick.
Varbergs awarded a free kick in their own half.
That's full-time at Strandvallen. The final score is 2-3.
Robin Tranberg is writhing in pain and play has been suspended for a few moments.
